I"Ï	<p>I am an expat living in Bangkok and rely on public transportation to avoid high traffic of Bangkok. I like to read/think and text during the daily commute to the office. As for commuting to a destination disconnected to train or bus, I have to use public taxi to get there. Lately, I‚Äôve been using Uber instead of public taxi service for these reasons:</p>

