<p>I ran into 2 blog entries that highlights some aspects about owning a car vs Uber or Lyft and decided to added some personal opinions. You can read the following entries to get some expert perspective and result of the research.</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://t.co/Ob1XclTPxD">People in Los Angeles Are Getting Rid Of Their Cars</a></li>
